        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Subcellular fractionation and immunoblotting for RabGDI from the rat brain shows enrichment of RabGDI in the LS2 fraction (presynaptic cytosol).. Experimental description: Materials and Methods: Isolation of synaptic organelles from rat brain homogenates. The methodologies for the isolation and characterization of highly purified rat SVs are based on our previously published protocols." ;
